findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The function excludeMultipleAccountsFromFees() uses a loop to exclude multiple accounts from fees and may be aborted with OUT_OF_GAS exception if there is a long addresses list.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges to modify critical parameters and access control lists, which can lead to unintended behavior or malicious activities.
